{{fr-adv}}

# [[not even]]
#: {{uxi|fr|Je ne sais '''même pas'''.|I '''don't even''' know.}}
#: {{ux|fr|Je veux '''même pas''' savoir.|I '''don't even''' want to know.}}

====Usage notes====
{{lang|fr|''Trésor de la langue française''}} states that the word order {{m|fr||pas même}} can be used without affecting the meaning of the phrase,<ref>{{R:fr:TLFi|pas}}</ref> but '''{{m|fr||même pas}}''' is considerably more common.
